<P>
BORDER PATROL (U.S.); UNITED STATES -- BORDERS -- MEXICO; ENDANGERED SPECIES; 
LIZARDS; ARCHEOLOGY -- MEXICO; HISTORIC SITES; PROPERTY DAMAGE; LAW ENFORCEMENT 
OFFICERS 
</P>
