<P>
DE VILAR, ALEXIS; ASSAULTS -- LOS ANGELES; BUSES; VIOLENCE; WRITERS; MURDERS -- 
CALIFORNIA; SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA RAPID TRANSIT DISTRICT 
</P>
