RESIGNATIONS; YELTSIN, BORIS N; KAZANNIK, ALEXEI I; CONGRESS OF PEOPLE'S 
DEPUTIES; GOVERNMENT REFORM; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; POLITICAL APPOINTMENTS; 
LUKYANOV, ANATOLY I 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
