<P>
EVANS NAMED HEAD OF UNITED ARTISTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times wire services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BEVERLY HILLS 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Qintex Entertainment Inc. said today it named David Evans president and chief 
executive officer of United Artists Corp. 
</P>
<P>
Qintex said the appointment is effective immediately and will be formalized 
after the completion this summer of its acquisition of United Artists. 
</P>
<P>
Qintex agreed on March 31 to acquire United Artists for about $1 billion. 
</P>
<P>
Evans was previously president and CEO of Qintex. 
